org.tron.trident.crypto.tuwenitypes

Class UInt256

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.tron.trident.crypto.tuwenitypes.UInt256
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<UInt256>, UInt256Value<UInt256>

    public final class UInt256
extends java.lang.Object
implements UInt256Value<UInt256>
    An unsigned 256-bit precision number. This is a raw UInt256Value - a 256-bit precision unsigned number of no particular unit.
